Problem:
Haha, tu n'y arriveras jamais... this old french men thinks he can troll us. He sends messages and messages again. Show him that you are awesome by breaking the message. Hint: Flag content should be lowercase. 



Solution:
The 'french man' hint tells us that the cipher is the Vigenère cipher. This cipher requires a keyword. Use a Vigenère cipher bruteforcer, https://www.dcode.fr/vigenere-cipher to decode the text into plaintext English. The flag is hidden in the decoded text, it needs to be formatted into lowercase before submission.
